synopsis: A young and talented architect comes to his senses after a horrific accident only to find himself in the odd dystopian world. synopsis: As Finn slips back into a groove of mindless parties, sunburn, and hangovers, he let's his life take a mind-numbing vacation. But when he's confronted with death first hand, he takes a new outlook on life, remembering his endless dreams and goals when he was young.  A micro-budget, DIY-minded, independent film incorporating elements from mumblecore and found footage cinema.
tagline: A portrait of a lost generation, seen through the mind of Finn, as he tries to find a new perspective and escape it.
